data.title: Western Movie Poster, J.W. Coop, 70s Poster Design
data.meta_description: Western movie poster with fabulous illustration by Czech poster designer Josef Duchoň, 1973. Discover his magnificent movie posters in our poster shop.
data.text:
Western movie poster with fantastic illustration.

title: J.W. Coop | USA, 1971

director: Cliff Robertson

with: Cliff Robertson, Geraldine Page, Cristina Ferrare

poster design: Josef Duchoň, 1973

Movie posters in our collection were promotional materials. Posters used on display in the cinemas across the former Czechoslovakia. They bear signs of their age.
